snippet.title: CYBERWAY - Synthwave game prototype with Godot Engine
snippet.description:
Endless driving game features a 1980s aesthetic with Synthwave soundtrack.
Play in browser: https://ggbot.itch.io/cyberway
If you like CYBERWAY, support this game at Itch.io

Music by Cool Cat Game Studio
